data.description: Move in Ready, Turnkey, Many upgrades, long canal view,  remodeled, new insulated roof panels over the screened porch, new plumbing & electrical panel box, structural tie downs added underneath every 5 feet around perimeter & up to code, new washer & dryer, new cabinets, new appliances,  kitchen island, open floor plan, Florida room has "Suntamers" window tint, fruit trees, New elevated A/C unit, new duct work. Pavers in front for extra parking of cars. Estero Bay is 7 minutes away by boat w/ fishing, beaches, shelling, waterfront restaurants, dolphin & manatees. The Gulf of Mexico is 15 minutes from the boat ramp via New Pass where Lovers Key State Park & Beach is located then head out for off-shore fishing in the Gulf. Amenity rich community with planned activities and social events, clubhouse, pool, spa hot tub, shuffleboard, tennis, pickle ball, boccie ball, basketball, fresh water lake, fishing pier, boat storage compound, doggie park. Lots are owned  & Low HOA fees. Great location, restaurants, public golf courses, Coconut Point Mall, Lee Medical Center in minutes, SW Florida International Airport, FGCU, I-75, and 41 are conveniently located.   Hurry this home will not last!
